p.value: Materials are open to researchers. Please contact the Tamiment Library & Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives for more information and to schedule an appointment, tamiment.wagner@nyu.edu or 212-998-2630.

An inventory of Boxes 2-11 of the collection, containing video and film material used in production of the film is available (see Box List).  The remaining boxes contain paper records, photographs, graphics, and audio materials.
